## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a4588-103">將 <xref:System.SerializableAttribute> 屬性套用至某個類型，以表示此類型的執行個體為可序列化。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a4588-103">Apply the <xref:System.SerializableAttribute> attribute to a type to indicate that instances of this type can be serialized.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a4588-104">Common language runtime 會擲回<xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationException>如果任何一種圖形中要序列化的物件沒有<xref:System.SerializableAttribute>套用的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a4588-104">The common language runtime throws <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationException> if any type in the graph of objects being serialized does not have the <xref:System.SerializableAttribute> attribute applied.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a4588-105">套用<xref:System.SerializableAttribute>屬性即使類別也實作<xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable>介面，以控制序列化程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a4588-105">Apply the <xref:System.SerializableAttribute> attribute even if the class also implements the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable> interface to control the serialization process.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a4588-106">當您將套用<xref:System.SerializableAttribute>屬性型別，預設序列化所有的私人和公用欄位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a4588-106">When you apply the <xref:System.SerializableAttribute> attribute to a type, all private and public fields are serialized by default.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a4588-107">您可以藉由實作更細微地控制序列化<xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable>介面，以覆寫序列化程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a4588-107">You can control serialization more granularly by implementing the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable> interface to override the serialization process.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a4588-108">您可以從序列化排除欄位，藉由套用或<xref:System.NonSerializedAttribute>屬性欄位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a4588-108">Or you can exclude fields from serialization by applying the <xref:System.NonSerializedAttribute> attribute to the field.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a4588-109">如果可序列化型別的欄位包含指標、 控制代碼或屬於特定的環境，且不能在不同環境中，有意義地還原某些其他資料結構，則您可能想要套用<xref:System.NonSerializedAttribute>屬性該欄位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a4588-109">If a field of a serializable type contains a pointer, a handle, or some other data structure that is specific to a particular environment, and cannot be meaningfully reconstituted in a different environment, then you might want to apply the <xref:System.NonSerializedAttribute> attribute to that field.</span></span>  
  
